given an array arr representing the powers of players, each player can fight with other player having less power and can take it power.
Find all possible players who can win the tournament by eliminating other players.

ex :
        int[] array1  = {2,3,4};
            sol : 2 beats 3 and the becomes 5 which collectively can beat 4;
            o/p 3 (3,4 can be come champ)
        int[] array2= {1,1,1};
            sol : any one of above can beat each other and become cham so o/p - 3.
        int[] arr3 = {2,2,10,10};
            sol : o/p : 10,10.